<tr><td colspan=2>Joined <span data-xutime='992502000'>06-14-01</span>, id: 80745, Profile Updated: <span data-xutime='1450913422'>12-23-15</span> <img ALIGN='ABSMIDDLE' src='/static/flags2/us.png' width=16 height=11 title='USA'> </td></tr></table><div id=bio style='padding-left:5px;padding-right:5px;'><img class='lazy cimage ' style='clear:left;float:left;margin-right:3px;padding:2px;border:1px solid #ccc;-moz-border-radius:2px;-webkit-border-radius:2px;' src='/static/images/d_60_90.jpg' data-original='//ffcdn2012t-fictionpressllc.netdna-ssl.com/image/1816330/150/' width=150 height=200><div style='padding-left:5px;margin-top:5px;'>Author has written 104 stories for Ranma, Misc. Games, Spirited Away, Matrix, Harry Potter, Series Of Unfortunate Events, Incredibles, Artemis Fowl, One Piece, Phineas and Ferb, Scooby Doo, Firefly, Gravity Falls, Wicked, Jumanji, Steven Universe, and Meet the Robinsons.</div><p>Interested in anime, Japanese, and adventure/puzzle games like Myst. Besides the series I have written stories for, I also enjoy the works of Gene Wolfe (<em>The Book of the New Sun</em>, etc.).</p><p>My avatar is an illustration for "A Series of Incredible Events," in which the Parr children become like the Baudelaires.</p><p><strong>Potionate Series</strong></p><p>AU's where the love potions of the Love God changed the lives of the Pines.</p><p>1) <a title="Potionate" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/10848039/1/Potionate" target="_blank">Potionate</a> -- Mabel and Pacifica<br>2) <a title="Potion Nullified" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11026313/1/Potion-Nullified" target="_blank">Potion Nullified</a> -- Robbie and Tambry get anti-love<br>3) <a title="Potion Triangulated" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/10968843/1/Potion-Triangulated" target="_blank">Potion Triangulated</a> -- Mabel, Pacifica, and Grenda<br>4) <a title="Potion Explosion" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11016058/1/Potion-Explosion" target="_blank">Potion Explosion</a> -- Dipper and Robbie<br>5) <a title="Potion Power" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11029331/1/Potion-Power" target="_blank">Potion Power</a> -- Robbie and Mabel (one-sided), and others in the teen group<br>6) <a title="Potion Punishment" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11035003/1/Potion-Punishment" target="_blank">Potion Punishment, Potion Nightmare</a> -- Mabel and Dipper (one-sided), Mabel and Bill<br>7) <a title="Potion Beastly" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11024086/1/Potion-Beastly" target="_blank">Potion Beastly</a> -- inter-species matches<br>8) <a title="Potion Revenge" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11042944/1/Potion-Revenge" target="_blank">Potion Revenge</a> -- Mabel and Gideon<br>9) <a title="Potion Purple" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11058914/1/Potion-Purple" target="_blank">Potion Purple</a> -- Dipper and Tambry<br>10) <a title="Potion Noir" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11073002/1/Potion-Noir" target="_blank">Potion Noir</a> -- Dipper and Pacifica<br>11) <a title="Potion Twins" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11085064/1/Potion-Twins" target="_blank">Potion Twins</a> -- Mabel, Dipper, and Pacifica<br>12) <a title="Potion Pooled" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11121637/1/Potion-Pooled" target="_blank">Potion Pooled</a> -- Mabel and Mermando, Dipper and Wendy<br>13) <a title="Potion Girls" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11317408/1/Potion-Girls" target="_blank">Potion Girls</a> -- Mabel, Wendy, and Pacifica<br>14) <a title="Potion Pines" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11522126/1/Potion-Pines" target="_blank">Potion Pines</a> -- Mabel and Dipper<br>15) <a title="Potion Harem" href="https://www.fanfiction.net/s/11685846/1/Potion-Harem">Potion Harem</a> -- Dipper and Wendy, Mabel, Tambry, Pacifica, Grenda, and Candy</p></div></TD></TR></TABLE>    <style>
